OL,3,CSilent bite: How shrinkflation is
OL,4,Cslimming down your Christmas classics
OL,6,FFrom April, retailers will be forced
OL,7,Fto display clearer unit pricing, as
OL,8,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FFor many families, Christmas
OL,12,Ftraditions haven't changed, but the
OL,13,Fproducts on supermarket shelves
OL,14,Fcertainly have.
OL,16,FA wave of shrinkflation has swept
OL,17,Fthrough some of Britain's most-loved
OL,18,Ffestive treats, with weights dropping
OL,19,Fand prices rising across major brands.
