OL,3,CSilent bite: How shrinkflation is
OL,4,Cslimming down your Christmas classics
OL,6,FManufacturers say soaring production
OL,7,Fand ingredient costs have forced their
OL,8,Fhand, but shoppers say it feels like
OL,9,Fthey're getting less for more.
OL,11,FFor example, shoppers will find out
OL,12,Fthis year that they're getting 50g
OL,13,Fless chocolate than last Christmas.
OL,14,FWhile the new tub dropped from 600g to
OL,15,F550g, supermarket prices have
OL,16,Fincreased from #6 to #7.
OL,18,FNestle said changes to size and
OL,19,Fpricing are reviewed annually.
