OL,3,CSilent bite: How shrinkflation is
OL,4,Cslimming down your Christmas classics
OL,6,FIn a statement, the company said its
OL,7,F2025 range is based on "a range of
OL,8,Ffactors including the cost of
OL,9,Fmanufacturing, ingredients, transport,
OL,10,Fand customer preferences."
OL,12,FNestle is not the only chocolate tin
OL,13,Fthat feels slightly lighter this year.
OL,15,FMars Wrigley's Celebrations have seen
OL,16,Ftwo consecutive reductions in two
OL,17,Fyears. In 2023, a Celebrations tub
OL,18,Fweighed in at 600g.
OL,20,FA reduction of 50g each year has been
OL,21,Fcut, leaving this year's tub at 500g.
