OL,3,CSilent bite: How shrinkflation is
OL,4,Cslimming down your Christmas classics
OL,6,FAlthough some retailers offer
OL,7,Fpromotions at varying times, in 2024 a
OL,8,Ftub of Celebrations cost #6 and has
OL,9,Frisen to #7 this year.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Mars Wrigley said it
OL,12,Ftries to "absorb pricing pressures
OL,13,Fwhere we can," but cited rising
OL,14,Fmanufacturing costs and "well-
OL,15,Fdocumented increases in the cost of
OL,16,Fcocoa" as reasons for its size
OL,17,Freductions.
OL,19,FThe company stressed the decision "is
OL,20,Fnot one we take lightly".
