OL,3,CSilent bite: How shrinkflation is
OL,4,Cslimming down your Christmas classics
OL,6,FMondelez has also slimmed down its
OL,7,Fseasonal favourite, Toblerone. The
OL,8,Ficonic triangular bar has dropped from
OL,9,F360g to 340g this year, while prices
OL,10,Fhave risen. Mondelez said shrinking
OL,11,Fproduct sizes is "a last resort".
OL,13,FAdding that "manufacturing and supply
OL,14,Fchain costs have increased
OL,15,Fsignificantly in recent years, and
OL,16,Fmany of our products have become more
OL,17,Fexpensive to make as a result."
