OL,11,FFood content creator, Tahnee Beck, has
OL,12,Falso noticed that the size of the
OL,13,FChristmas tubs has reduced over the
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FBeck told ITV News: "The tubs have
OL,17,Fgone down from 600g to 550g, you're
OL,18,Fprobably losing four or five
OL,19,Fchocolates a tub.
