OL,3,CSilent bite: How shrinkflation is
OL,4,Cslimming down your Christmas classics
OL,6,F"Families are already under huge
OL,7,Fpressure at Christmas, so paying more
OL,8,Ffor smaller tubs really does make a
OL,9,Fdifference."
OL,11,FAs frustration over shrinking products
OL,12,Fgrows, some countries have already
OL,13,Ftaken steps to force greater
OL,14,Ftransparency.
OL,16,FAccording to John Wilks, an
OL,17,Fadvertising and consumer law
OL,18,Fspecialist at DLA Piper, a few
OL,19,Fgovernments are moving faster than
OL,20,Fothers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]
