OL,3,CSilent bite: How shrinkflation is
OL,4,Cslimming down your Christmas classics
OL,6,F"There's a small group of countries
OL,7,Fthat are really the front runners;
OL,8,FItaly, France, Hungary and Romania.
OL,10,F"They've already introduced
OL,11,Flegislation requiring retailers to
OL,12,Fidentify when a product has been
OL,13,Fshrinkflated," Wilks said.
OL,15,FThe UK is also tightening its rules.
OL,16,FFrom April, new transparency
OL,17,Frequirements will force retailers to
OL,18,Fdisplay clearer unit pricing.
OL,20,FThis move is designed to help shoppers
OL,21,Fcompare products more easily.
